2. Epitaph for Biktoria","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q7KT855P\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q7KT855P\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βικτωρία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βικτωρία\">Βικτωρία\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>χρηστὰ καὶ \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ἄμεμπτε χαῖ-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ρε ἔζησε ἔτη \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">κε\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>ἷς ἄν τούτῳ ἐπιβου-\u003Cbr id=\"al7-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>[λ]εύσηται τῷ μνημίῳ \u003Cspan data-text=\"δ\n                    οὲ\">δ-\u003Cbr id=\"al8-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>ο\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"οαὐτὸν\">οὐτὸν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ὅρκος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὅρκος\">Ὅρκος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἀπο{ο}λεῖ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.6 reg., orig. ἷς | l.8 reg., orig. Δ Οο | reg., orig. ΟΥΤῸΝο\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q7KT855P\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q7KT855P\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βικτωρία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βικτωρία\">ΒΙΚΤΩΡΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΧΡΗΣΤΑΚΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΑΜΕΜΠΤΕΧΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΡΕΕΖΗΣΕΕΤΗ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ΚΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>ΙΣΑΝΤΟΥΤΩΕΠΙΒΟΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al7-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>[.]ΕΥΣΗΤΑΙΤΩΜΝΗΜΙΩ\u003Cspan data-text=\"δ\n                    οὲ\">Δ\u003Cbr id=\"al8-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>Ο\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"οαὐτὸν\">ΟΥΤΟΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ὅρκος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὅρκος\">ΟΡΚΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΑΠΟΟΛΕΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.6 reg., orig. ἷς | l.8 reg., orig. Δ Οο | reg., orig. ΟΥΤῸΝο\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text of Manganaro\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Biktoria, worthy and blameless, lived 25 years. Whoever tampers with this memorial, Horkos will destroy them.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The first editors assumed that the second part of the text was perhaps written at a different time / by a different hand, but Manganaro assumes the role of a workshop in preparing the 'standard' imprecation below the tablet. In any case, the difference between the larger marble letters and the smaller letters cut onto the limestone base is already sufficient explanation for any difference. Manganaro rightly comments on the selective use of the more precious marble (this practice more familiar from statue bases). The final line is of very uncertain interpretation, appearing to show multiple errors in carving.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Arias NSA 1937 467-468 no.13 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1941 199-200 no.72 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1962 500-501 fig.9 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001851\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001851\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>lunate epsilon and sigma; uncial omega.\u003C/p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[190,193,196,199,202,205,208,211],{"id":191,"html":192},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://ww