 lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βικτωρία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βικτωρία\">ΒΙΚΤΩΡΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΧΡΗΣΤΑΚΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΑΜΕΜΠΤΕΧΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΡΕΕΖΗΣΕΕΤΗ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ΚΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>ΙΣΑΝΤΟΥΤΩΕΠΙΒΟΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al7-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>[.]ΕΥΣΗΤΑΙΤΩΜΝΗΜΙΩ\u003Cspan data-text=\"δ\n                    οὲ\">Δ\u003Cbr id=\"al8-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>Ο\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"οαὐτὸν\">ΟΥΤΟΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ὅρκος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὅρκος\">ΟΡΚΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΑΠΟΟΛΕΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.6 reg., orig. ἷς | l.8 reg., orig. Δ Οο | reg., orig. ΟΥΤῸΝο\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":194,"html":195},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>",{"id":197,"html":198},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text of Manganaro\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":200,"html":201},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Biktoria, worthy and blameless, lived 25 years. Whoever tampers with this memorial, Horkos will destroy them.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":203,"html":204},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The first editors assumed that the second part of the text was perhaps written at a different time / by a different hand, but Manganaro assumes the role of a workshop in preparing the 'standard' imprecation below the tablet. In any case, the difference between the larger marble letters and the smaller letters cut onto the limestone base is already sufficient explanation for any difference. Manganaro rightly comments on the selective use of the more precious marble (this practice more familiar from statue bases). The final line is of very uncertain interpretation, appearing to show multiple errors in carving.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":206,"html":207},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Arias NSA 1937 467-468 no.13 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1941 199-200 no.72 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1962 500-501 fig.9 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001851\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001851\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":209,"html":210},"handnote","\u003Cp>lunate epsilon and sigma; uncial omega.\u003C/p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":212,"html":213},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[215,217,220,221],{"html":216},"Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q7KT855P\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q7KT855P\u003C/a>",{"id":218,"lang":109,"html":219},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βικτωρία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βικτωρία\">Βικτωρία\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>χρηστὰ καὶ \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ἄμεμπτε χαῖ-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ρε ἔζησε ἔτη \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">κε\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>ἷς ἄν τούτῳ ἐπιβου-\u003Cbr id=\"al7-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>[λ]εύσηται τῷ μνημίῳ \u003Cspan data-text=\"δ\n                    οὲ\">δ-\u003Cbr id=\"al8-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>ο\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"οαὐτὸν\">οὐτὸν\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ὅρκος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὅρκος\">Ὅρκος\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἀπο{ο}λεῖ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.6 reg., orig. ἷς | l.8 reg., orig. Δ Οο | reg., orig. ΟΥΤῸΝο\u003C/p>",{"html":216},{"id":222,"lang":109,"html":223},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βικτωρία\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βικτωρία\">ΒΙΚΤΩΡΙΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΧΡΗΣΤΑΚΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΑΜΕΜΠΤΕΧΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΡΕΕΖΗΣΕΕΤΗ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ΚΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>ΙΣΑΝΤΟΥΤΩΕΠΙΒΟΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al7-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>[.]ΕΥΣΗΤΑΙΤΩΜΝΗΜΙΩ\u003Cspan data-text=\"δ\n                    οὲ\">Δ\u003Cbr id=\"al8-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">8\u003C/span>Ο\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"οαὐτὸν\">ΟΥΤΟΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ὅρκος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὅρκος\">ΟΡΚΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΑΠΟΟΛΕΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.6 reg., orig. ἷς | l.8 reg., orig. Δ Οο | reg., orig. ΟΥΤῸΝο\u003C/p>",[],[226],{"html":59},"\u003C?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"https://epidoc.stoa.org/schema/latest/tei-epidoc.rng\" type=\"application/xml\" schematypens=\"http://relaxng.org/ns/structure/1.0\"?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"../schematron/ircyr-checking.sch\" schematypens=\"http://purl.oclc.org/dsdl/schematron\"?>\n\u003CTEI xmlns=\"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n    \u003CteiHeader>\n        \u003CfileDesc>\n            \u003CtitleStmt>\n                \u003Ctitle>Epitaph for Biktoria\u003C/title>\n                \u003Ceditor ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/editor>\n                \u003Cprincipal ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/principal>\n                \u003Cfunder>John Fell OUP Research Fund\u003C/funder>\n\t   \u003Cfunder>\u003Cref target=\"https://cordis.europa.eu/project/id/885040\">ERC Advanced Grant no.885040\u003C/ref>\u003C/funder>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JP\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>original data collection and editing\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JCu\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0002-6686-3728\">James Cummings\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>conversion to EpiDoc\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n\t    \u003CrespStmt>\n     \t       \u003Cname xml:id=\"SS\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569\">Simona Stoyanova\u003C/name>\n     \t       \u003Cresp>standardisation of template and tidying up encoding\u003C/resp>\n \t   \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"ZL\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0009-0007-0586-7956\">Zoé Lienard\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>named entity annotation\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n            \u003C/titleStmt>\n            \u003CpublicationStmt>\n                \u003Cauthority>I.Sicily\u003C/authority>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"filename\">ISic003432\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"TM\">644827\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDR\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDH\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDCS\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"PHI\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"URI\">http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003432\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"DOI\" when=\"2020-12-23\">10.5281/zenodo.4388568\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cavailability>\n                    \u003Clicence target=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.\u003C/licence>\n                \u003C/availability>\n            \u003C/publicationStmt>\n            \u003CsourceDesc>\n                \u003CmsDesc>\n                    \u003CmsIdentifier>\n                        \u003Ccountry>Italy\u003C/country>\n                        \u003Cregion>Sicily\u003C/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>Comiso\u003C/settlement>\n                        \u003Crepository role=\"other\">Scuola di Arte\u003C/repository>\n                        \u003C!--No inventory number found-->\n                        \u003C!--Adding location for old id numbers if available-->\n                        \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement/>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/textLang>\n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\u003Cp>A cippus of the local limestone, quadrangular in section, damaged above and below (mouldings lost), with a marble plaque (21x26cm) inserted into the face, and with a further text inscribed below on the front face of the cippus.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial type=\"inorganic.stone\" subtype=\"unverified\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html\">limestone and marble\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.stele\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/250.html\">stele\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">51\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">24.5\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\"/>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition/>\n\t\t    \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\u003Cp>First five lines of text centred on marble plaque, with little respect for word-division; three continuous lines immediately below.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                \t\u003Cdamage/>\n\t\t\t\u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\u003Cp>lunate epsilon and sigma; uncial omega.\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462185\">Dianae Fons\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/2524955\">Comiso\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003Cgeo>36.94893, 14.60731\u003C/geo>\n                            \u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"0201\" notAfter-custom=\"0300\" evidence=\"lettering archaeological-context\">3rd century CE\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\">Recovered in 1934 from a tomb in the necropolis under via Tenente Meli, Comiso\u003Cgeo>36.9449201,14.6053767\u003C/geo>; observed by Manganaro c.1962 in the entranceway to the Scuola di Arte, Comiso\u003C/provenance>\u003C!-- location of the tomb according to the Plan in Arias 1937 fig.1 -->\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">None\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n             \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n             \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                 \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                     \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                 \u003C/xi:fallback>\n             \u003C/xi:include>\n\t  \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n\t     \u003Cxi:fallback>\n\t       \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>\n\t     \u003C/xi:fallback>\n\t   \u003C/xi:include>\n         \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    \u003Cp>Julian Calendar\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/calendar>\n            \u003C/calendarDesc>\n            \u003ClangUsage>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"en\">English\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"it\">Italian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"osc\">Oscan\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xly\">Elymian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"sxc\">Sikan\u003C/language>\n            \u003C/langUsage>\n            \u003CtextClass>\n                \u003Ckeywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    \u003Cterm ana=\"#function.funerary\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html\">funerary\u003C/term>\n                \u003C/keywords>\n            \u003C/textClass>\n        \u003C/profileDesc>\n        \u003CrevisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            \u003ClistChange>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n            \t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-23\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-11-28\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised from publications\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2026-02-11\" who=\"#ZL\">tagged names and persons\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\u003Csurface/>\u003C!-- \n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic003432_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic003432.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface> -->\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#JP\" source=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q7KT855P\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>Βικτωρία\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>χρηστὰ καὶ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>ἄμεμπτε χαῖ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\" break=\"no\"/>ρε ἔζησε ἔτη\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>\u003Chi rend=\"supraline\">κε\u003C/hi>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\"/>\u003Cchoice>\u003Corig>ἷς\u003C/orig>\u003Creg>εἷς\u003C/reg>\u003C/choice> ἄν τούτῳ ἐπιβου\n                    \u003Clb n=\"7\" break=\"no\"/>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">λ\u003C/supplied>εύσηται τῷ μνημίῳ \u003Cw>δ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"8\" break=\"no\"/>\u003Cchoice>\u003Corig>ο\u003C/orig>\u003Creg>ὲ\u003C/reg>\u003C/choice>\u003C/w> \u003Cw>\u003Cchoice>\u003Corig>ο\u003C/orig>\u003Creg>α\u003C/reg>\u003C/choice>ὐτὸν\u003C/w> \u003CpersName type=\"divine\">\u003Cname>Ὅρκος\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>  ἀπο\u003Csurplus>ο\u003C/surplus>λεῖ \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text of Manganaro\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Biktoria, worthy and blameless, lived 25 years. Whoever tampers with this memorial, Horkos will destroy them.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>The first editors assumed that the second part of the text was perhaps written at a different time / by a different hand, but Manganaro assumes the role of a workshop in preparing the 'standard' imprecation below the tablet. In any case, the difference between the larger marble letters and the smaller letters cut onto the limestone base is already sufficient explanation for any difference. Manganaro rightly comments on the selective use of the more precious marble (this practice more familiar from statue bases). The final line is of very uncertain interpretation, appearing to show multiple errors in carving.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"NSA\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Arias\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Ctitle>NSA\u003C/title>\n                        \u003Cdate>1937\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>467-468 no.13\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Ferrua\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1941\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>199-200 no.72\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4HR4GXBX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001456\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1962\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>500-501 fig.9\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q7KT855P\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001851\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001851\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
